import React from 'react';

import Books from './Bookinfos'
import BookForm from './CreateBook'
import { Grommet, Heading,Box,grommet,Grid } from 'grommet'


function MyBookinfo (){
return(
<Grommet theme={grommet} full >
      <Grid fill rows={["auto", "flex", "auto"]}>
      <Box align="center" tag="header" background="#00739D" pad="medium" color="#00739D">
      <Heading margin="none" color="#F2F2F2">My BookInfo</Heading>
      </Box>

   
      <Books/>   
       <BookForm/> 
       

        <Box flex={false} tag="footer" background="#00739D" pad="medium">
      <Heading margin="none" size="small"></Heading>
      </Box>
      </Grid>
    </Grommet>
)
}

export default MyBookinfo
